Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的晚霞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以得多少分？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给晚霞打分？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 晚霞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,65分左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,95分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么少了5分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没能听完你的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为是他 是浩平在吹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要等他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是第一次来这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岬学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在失明以前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于住在这附近的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个学校是自己的梦想所在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是向往已久的游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让老师和管理员们发现 我常偷偷溜进来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 这里是让我安心的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他 把我带入了一个崭新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的... 约定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的毕业典礼上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会作为在校生的代表为我吹奏一曲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和我约定过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 约定...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到长笛的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道自己所等的一定就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要带我来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天 第三天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直遵照约定在此等你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我还会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就先借给你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:17:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是借给你哦 一定要还我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天的... 约定...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美纱绪...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不记得我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 还记得你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折原 浩平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美纱绪...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:19:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么永远
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着更为重要的约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耽误了你这么长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能永远不会再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他必须动身前往「永远」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 折原浩平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪了我一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须动身前往「永远」...
